column2: You must defeat the Mursaat Overseer game piece to purchase this item.

Unlocks all recipes needed to craft Forgotten Brilliance.

Braham has gone after Svanir in the Shiverpeaks. What better opportunity to kill two birds with one stone: recruit him to Dragon's Watch, and find another corrupted sample for Taimi.
Rankings for the Bronze league of the 2004 WvW Tournament.

Summon the Mad Mirror to carry you along the ground. You will be removed from the travel toy if you engage in combat.

This item has no movement-speed bonus or additional skills.
Gather crab or cave beast meat to feed raptors, engage enemies while mounted, and hunt fireflies on your raptor.

Grants the ability to wield kodan fire magic based on a flame spirit that has been tamed since ancient times. Learning this Mastery will unlock the first skill while carrying Koda's Flame. Visit kodan flamebearers to learn additional skills.
As long as a lord is in combat, or as long as team scores are identical, overtime will continue.
Used to craft Hardened Leather Gloves.
You've helped train or take care of a raptor.

Consuming this will unlock one random wardrobe option that you do not already own in the following categories:
* Equipment Skins (exotic or less)
* Outfits
* Dyes
* Gliders
* Minis
* Finishers
* Mail Carriers

Toss dung, preferably into a trash receptacle.
Gain vigor when successfully evading an attack.
Double-click to receive 1 Hairstyle Kit, 1 Zephyrite Color Swatch: green, 6 Transmutation Charges, 1 Top Hat skin, 5 Metabolic Primers, and 5 Utility Primers.
